    <ul class="reasons-list">
      <li><strong>CycleSaver plus cell-and-curtain architecture expertise.</strong> Hoshizaki KM-Edge has a water inlet pump (different from Manitowoc and Scotsman designs). We know the difference, and we don't misdiagnose Hoshizaki cycle times against the wrong baseline.</li>
